    <item>
      <title>纳格尔称欧洲央行无法解决债券市场的政治影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/ecb-can-t-solve-political-fallout-on-bond-markets-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员约阿希姆纳格尔表示，欧洲央行不会采取行动应对因政治风险引起的政府债券市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/ecb-can-t-solve-political-fallout-on-bond-markets-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 15:14:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大股市上涨 22% 后，Ned Davis 将评级上调至增持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-stocks-upgraded-to-overweight-by-ned-davis-after-22-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大股市的上涨促使 Ned Davis Research 敦促投资者通过将多伦多上市股票的评级上调至增持来增加对市场的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-stocks-upgraded-to-overweight-by-ned-davis-after-22-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>集团首席财务官表示，阿达尼绿色美元债券可能在 2025 年中期恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集团首席财务官 Jugeshinder Singh 周五表示，阿达尼绿色能源有限公司 (Adani Green Energy Ltd.) 将考虑在 4 月至 6 月期间重新发行已废除的美元债券，此举彰显了尽管美国对创始人 Gautam Adani 展开调查，该集团仍具有强大的韧性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 首次阿根廷私有化遭遇 5.36 亿美元债务困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/milei-s-first-privatization-in-argentina-beset-by-536-million-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 设定 12 月为阿根廷首次将大量国有企业出售给私营部门的最后期限，这表明政府出售企业将面临巨大挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/milei-s-first-privatization-in-argentina-beset-by-536-million-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦呼吁欧洲央行降息，因为通胀目标即将实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/villeroy-calls-for-ecb-rate-cuts-as-inflation-target-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行应继续降息，因为欧元区通胀率可能在 2025 年上半年达到 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/villeroy-calls-for-ecb-rate-cuts-as-inflation-target-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西资产将因预算计划遭遇两年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西股市有望迎来两年来最糟糕的一周，此前备受吹捧的削减政府开支计划令投资者感到失望，并加剧了人们对该国预算的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀加速但不会阻止欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管欧元区通胀率已超过欧洲央行 2% 的目标，但官员们不太可能在下个月及以后继续降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合信贷银行将与法国农业信贷银行讨论 Amundi 协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来几周，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 和法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 的高管将齐聚一堂，讨论意大利联合信贷银行收购国内竞争对手一事，届时两家公司之间还将讨论一项至关重要的分销协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 09:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市上涨，收益率在短线交易中下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国股市上涨，美国国债收益率下跌，而有关当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将缓和其最极端的贸易政策的猜测导致美元创下三个月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 22:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
